data.name: customCommandLabel2.Text
data.value:
@path@ The path to a single directory. If multiple directories are found, selected, and opened, your custom command will be called multiple times - once for each directory to be opened.
@list@ If multiple directories are found, selected, and opened, the entire list will be passed to your custom command and it will only be run once.
